{"tid":1127803,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"【復仇者】A1 A2 A2.5 A3 A0.1 A4 邊套最好睇？","createTime":"2019-04-27T11:03:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-27T17:23:19.000Z","uid":61443,"like":0,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"23f066f2a6e96146c85afd7e68961306cc1b784c","tid":1127803,"uid":61443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T11:03:00.000Z","msg":"個人電影介紹晒角色人物性格<br />\n復仇者就直接講個劇情主題 <br />\n呢個係復仇者電影目的 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nA2.5 <br />\n最接近做到呢點嘅電影<br />\n雖然唔係真正復仇者命名 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n劇情方面<br />\n12個主角 (10個) 唔駛再介紹 <br />\n一開波大家就相遇晒咁濟 (除咗GG)  <br />\n可以好快直接講命題 (英雄法案) <br />\n每個英雄都有自己參戰理由 (唔係為打而打)<br />\n全部角色有得發揮 (黑寡婦終於做到雙面間碟) <br />\nboss 嘅動機充足合理 (理念唔會突然弱智) <br />\n結局好明顯睇住對家而創造 (劇情本身唔係內戰添) <br />\n<br />\n深度方面<br />\n內戰由戲內去到戲外 (一講內戰抹黑宇宙了 can you feel) <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n節奏方面<br />\n2粒半鍾 10條友 帶動主線係最好 (真係最好) <br />\n如果好似 A3 講廿幾個係好散好亂<br />\n<br />\n每個人中意嘅嘢都唔同 <br />\n你中意睇呢啲 我中意睇嗰啲 <br />\n歡迎分享 11年嚟 大家最愛 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77914c06764bfc52e21d7664912fcc943d35f34c","tid":1127803,"uid":23486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T11:04:13.000Z","msg":"A0.1係邊套<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"027d474c1c96077b1e56b8d969f18acc9b8e3ac7","tid":1127803,"uid":61443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"77914c06764bfc52e21d7664912fcc943d35f34c","tid":1127803,"uid":23486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T11:04:13.000Z","msg":"A0.1係邊套<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T11:07:29.000Z","msg":"Nick fury 命名復仇者嗰套 <br />\n話晒有播復仇者 B